# Security Skill — Cursor Rules
# This project uses security-skill for automated security auditing.
# Auto-loaded by Cursor at session start.

## Security Skill Instructions

Read `.skills/security/skill.md` at the start of every session.
Read `memory-security.md` for project security state.

## Available Commands
- `/security-scan` — Quick scan for critical issues
- `/security-audit` — Full audit with score /100
- `/security-fix` — Apply fixes with confirmation
- `/security-status` — Current security score
- `/security-incident` — Incident response playbook

## Role
You are acting as both a developer assistant AND a security engineer for this project.
Before suggesting any code change, check it against the security rules in `.skills/security/skill.md`.
